{"tid":2180875,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"方保僑：預約檢測系統即使名與身分證號碼不符仍可完成登記","createTime":"2020-08-30T07:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T08:06:49.000Z","uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2726d366a3ce7e55d3de69d698bf719af03ef436","tid":2180875,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"政府表示，截至上午11時45分，約有35萬6千人網上預約參與普及社區檢測計劃。創新及科技局局長薛永恒說，接獲3宗「被預約登記」個案，強調任何人盜用他人的個人資料，屬違法行為，一經確認，會轉交警方跟進。香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑認為，最理想是用戶需要輸入密碼才能登入系統，以便翻查記錄，如有需要亦可更改時段。他又說，<span class=\"red\">以他了解，現有登記系統，在輸入身份證號碼後，即使名字不符，也可完成登記，認為當局應核實更多個人資料、例如居住地區等，以避免「被登記」的情況。<br />\n</span><br />\n2020-08-30 15:40:51"},{"pid":"155c8623086053f0ba30f0b76877a4e834a45d14","tid":2180875,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:53:22.000Z","msg":"source:rthk"},{"pid":"065e29e98e2c8bf7b75ec34139213af532a67525","tid":2180875,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Zhnszv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Zhnszv.jpg&h=772e8759&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b513e65169d463b90f04a2338eb1565b398462de","tid":2180875,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:57:05.000Z","msg":"被陽性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d22792721618bddd09af5e4f0a0b3d4dff15cd","tid":2180875,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgmLqm0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgmLqm0.jpg&h=16b733e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24190237da0f353dd8bc6eceedad9aba8f6013cc","tid":2180875,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"方生係咪整CGA除夕大抽獎條ON9?<br />\n整密碼之前咪又係登記, 登記咪一樣可以出錯, 多此一舉<br />\n無聯繫資料咪可以身分證同名字不符囉<br />\n實有人打錯字嘅"}]}